<section class="v4-page-shell"><div class="v4-page-head"><h1>SEO Audit Dashboard</h1><p>فحص سريع للأخبار والصفحات والتصنيفات، مع Score ومشكلات تحتاج متابعة.</p></div>
<div class="v4-kpi-strip"><div class="v4-kpi-card"><strong><?= (int)($audit['summary']['count'] ?? 0) ?></strong><span>العناصر المفحوصة</span></div><div class="v4-kpi-card"><strong><?= (int)($audit['summary']['average'] ?? 0) ?>/100</strong><span>المتوسط</span></div><div class="v4-kpi-card"><strong><?= (int)($audit['summary']['needs_work'] ?? 0) ?></strong><span>تحتاج تحسين</span></div></div>
<div class="v4-table-wrap"><table class="v4-table"><thead><tr><th>النوع</th><th>العنوان</th><th>Score</th><th>الرابط</th><th>Checks</th></tr></thead><tbody><?php foreach (($audit['items'] ?? []) as $item): ?><tr><td><?= e($item['type'] ?? '') ?></td><td><?= e($item['title'] ?? '') ?></td><td><span class="v4-score v4-score-<?= (($item['score'] ?? 0) >= 90) ? 'good' : ((($item['score'] ?? 0) >= 70) ? 'mid' : 'bad') ?>"><?= (int)($item['score'] ?? 0) ?></span></td><td><?php if (!empty($item['url'])): ?><a href="<?= e($item['url']) ?>" target="_blank" rel="noopener">فتح</a><?php endif; ?></td><td><ul class="v4-check-list"><?php foreach (($item['checks'] ?? []) as $check): ?><li class="v4-check-<?= e($check['status'] ?? 'warn') ?>"><strong><?= e($check['label'] ?? '') ?>:</strong> <?= e($check['message'] ?? '') ?></li><?php endforeach; ?></ul></td></tr><?php endforeach; ?></tbody></table></div></section>
